Archival Materials:
The exhibition Just Above Midtown:
Changing Spaces includes archival
posters, postcards, calendars, 35mm
slides of artists' work, photographs,
video footage, bills, receipts, and
correspondence between the gallery
and various parties, including artists,
printers, shipping companies, debt.
collectors, lenders, foundations, and
museums. The majority of this material is
on loan from the Just Above Midtown Gallery.
Records, Collection Linda Goode Bryant,
New York. A selection is listed below.
